snippet.title: TOP HIGHLIGHTS of FUNNY PUPPIES that will make you LAUGH - Funny DOG compilation
snippet.description:
These puppies are the best and the funniest, they are much funnier than cats! This is the hardest try not to laugh challenge in the World! Just look how all these cute puppies behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
